title: Burden to Bear Chapter 11!
body:
From The beginning | Newest Chapter

This chapter: The conclusion of the sports festival is finally here!

Premise:

DadMight AU in which Izuku is actually All Might’s son, and knows it, but All Might hasn’t allowed the information to go public. Izuku knows why it’s always been a secret, but there is some part of him that wonders if there is more to it than just protecting him and his mom. Izuku is believed to be quirkless before receiving One for All, but actually isn’t.

body:
Midoriya: Guys! Guys, let's take a vote.
Uraraka: Secret vote. Everybody close your eyes.
Everyone: *they all cover their eyes*
Asui: We won't know the results.
Iida: Well, say your vote out loud.
Kirishima: We'll know each other's voices.
Todoroki: Bakugo's got a point.

question: hey sweetie, love the blog. i saw your post where you mentioned boundaries and consent and i wanted to ask if everything is okay? i understand if your uncomfortable saying but know we're all here for you and love you. <3
answer:
Hiyaa, thanks for the concern but I’m okay.

It happened in the past and it’s something I’m working through at the moment. I really appreciate the support though, it means a great deal :’))

question: Aoyama
answer:
My sparkle boi!!!!

I love him and I could literally talk about him for hours.

My HC for him is that he’s a super foodie! He has a sophisticated palate and enjoys going out to eat delicacies. While he agrees that Lunch Rush’s food is delicious it doesn’t satisfy him. He usually goes out to after classes with Iida, Todoroki, and Yaoyarozu to get dinner. Fancy kid squad.
